			subtitle: "The Starlight Pool. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"A Lightwell, when given items such as Aquamarine or Rock Crystals, will create Liquid Starlight from them."
				""
				"Liquid Starlight will have plenty of uses in the future."
				""
				"Note that, by using magma/netherrack or packed ice/ice instead of the rockcrystal/aquamarine, you'll receive lava/water."
				""
				"As Direwolf would say, 'neat!'"
			]
