			subtitle: "Iron, but it's linked to the stars. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"By linking the Starlight from a Collector Crystal, or another source, to some Iron ore, you can obtain Starmetal ore, which can be further melted into Starmetal Ingots."
				""
