			description: [
				"The Tainted Blood Pendant is a curio added by Botania. When worn in the Curio Amulet slot, it will give the potion effect infused into the pendant for the duration of 4 seconds (14 seconds for Night Vision) every 4 seconds, given that the wearer has a mana source in he's/her's inventory."
